{"tid":939103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那香港聯絡辦公室接見非法組織代表","createTime":"2018-12-13T00:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T02:40:31.000Z","uid":51271,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b96ecbeb5161475a412f328735d0522291534d1c","tid":939103,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:00:24.000Z","msg":"【加拿大前外交官被拘留 外交部：組織違法】<br />\n【中聯部被揭曾接見康明凱　惟報道已經被刪】<br />\n<br />\n加拿大前外交官康明凱周一晚上在北京被拘留，中國外交部發言人回應指，康明凱任職的機構國際危機組織，在中國沒有備案，他在中國活動屬於違法。<br />\n<br />\n不過在中聯部的官網上，曾經報道過副部長郭業洲在今年8月接見過康明凱並交換意見，當時康明凱是以組織代表身份出席，但網頁現在已經被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n#康明凱<br />\n#加拿大<br />\n#外交官<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"0b30048e31b3a0d26dce478aa411bfa7f881e601","tid":939103,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n贏国冇野多，法例最多<br />\n平時冇事，想整你就會搵到條罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621a8cd25ec986d9cf14e3e1d3e425c4516051d1","tid":939103,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"千辛萬苦先諗到條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21d7dcb4348de41d90ad03ccb3c4fac92994a43","tid":939103,"uid":29804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:05:58.000Z","msg":"中聯部<br />\n<br />\n唔係中聯辦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bab0b4f729a706ed5f7895648edf7d6d6ffa77","tid":939103,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"之前條友上過tvb清心直說<br />\nTvb接見非法組織代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed90eaee7e